ization\", \"from\": 7246, \"to\": 7266}, {\"ngram\": \"exceptional interest\", \"from\": 7273, \"to\": 7293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that \\\"exceptional interest\\\" never materialized for France.\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7352, \"end\": 7358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720861363756, \"rank\": 1.573880661364224e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exceptional interest\", \"from\": 7307, \"to\": 7327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The European championship, known as EuroBasket, was in September 2022, and when the French officials and Embiid began discussing a passport the previous spring, Team France wanted Embiid in the fold for that.Nikola Joki\\u0107,Giannis AntetokounmpoandLuka Don\\u010di\\u0107were among the NBA stars playing for their respective home countries.\", \"from\": 7361, \"to\": 7686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7445, \"end\": 7451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9230632256575294, \"rank\": 0.08278875133142585, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 7522, \"end\": 7533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9906834371812456, \"rank\": 0.00940417742893011, \"text\": \"Team France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7632, \"end\": 7635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.232150005396003e-39, \"text\": \"N