ookie season\", \"from\": 9370, \"to\": 9387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lacking the passion and focus that had carried them in China, Tokyo and Berlin, the French failed to get out of pool play.\", \"from\": 9415, \"to\": 9537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9470, \"end\": 9475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6428318116136508, \"rank\": 0.5208169729642699, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9477, \"end\": 9482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999994206519, \"rank\": 5.796619584892996e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 9487, \"end\": 9493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.999984249108266, \"rank\": 1.575113996651637e-05, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}, {\"begin\": 9499, \"end\": 9505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9230632256575294, \"rank\": 0.08278875133142585, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the passion\", \"from\": 9423, \"to\": 9434}, {\"ngram\": \"pool play\", \"from\": 9527, \"to\": 9536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team France was on the clock for Paris, and in a September news conference after returning home from the World Cup, Siutat set an Oct. 10 deadline for Embiid.\", \"from\": 9539, \"to\": 9697, \"enti